{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.13\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大衛的詩。交給聖詠團長。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">求耶和華看顧</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和華啊，你忘記我要到幾時呢？要到永遠嗎？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">你轉臉不顧我要到幾時呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>我心裏籌算，終日愁苦，要到幾時呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">我的仇敵升高壓制我，要到幾時呢？</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>耶和華－我的上帝啊，求你看顧我，應允我！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">求你使我眼目明亮，免得我沉睡至死；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>免得我的仇敵說「我勝了他」；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">免得我的敵人在我動搖的時候喜樂。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>但我倚靠你的慈愛，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">我的心因你的救恩快樂。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.13.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>我要向耶和華歌唱，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">因他厚厚地恩待我。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}